      <title>南非兰特上涨，Godongwana 保留财政职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/south-african-rand-rallies-as-godongwana-retains-finance-post</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨 (Cyril Ramaphosa) 宣布新内阁并将优先考虑快速和可持续增长后，南非兰特延续了选举后的涨势。]]></description>
