    <item>
      <title>黎智英儿子称外国法官应退出香港法庭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/jimmy-lai-s-son-says-foreign-judges-should-quit-hong-kong-bench</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前媒体大亨黎智英的儿子呼吁所有外国法官离开香港的司法体系，给他们施加更大压力，迫使他们加入这股外逃大潮，这可能会削弱香港与中国内地之间的一个关键区别。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/jimmy-lai-s-son-says-foreign-judges-should-quit-hong-kong-bench</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 06:22:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙与法国左翼对手竞相阻止勒庞势头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/macron-and-french-left-wing-rivals-race-to-stop-far-right-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的中间派联盟和左翼新人民阵线正在考虑是否将候选人从周日的第二轮立法选举中撤出，以阻止崛起的极右翼国民联盟掌权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/macron-and-french-left-wing-rivals-race-to-stop-far-right-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 05:49:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾警告中国可能加大拘押力度，向赖昌星施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/china-to-step-up-detentions-to-squeeze-lai-taiwan-officials-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾官员表示，他们担心中国将拘留更多岛内人士，以对总统赖清德施加压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/china-to-step-up-detentions-to-squeeze-lai-taiwan-officials-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 05:49:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度反对党和律师猛烈抨击新刑法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/india-opposition-parties-lawyers-hit-out-at-new-criminal-laws</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度反对派团体和律师对新刑法的出台表示担忧，称这些变化实施得太仓促，而且没有经过适当协商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/india-opposition-parties-lawyers-hit-out-at-new-criminal-laws</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 05:43:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛认为南非“脆弱”的联盟将刺激经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/south-africa-elections-opposition-makes-debut-in-ramaphosa-s-unity-cabinet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨宣布了新内阁，将部长职位分配给亲商的反对派政客，同时保留亲密盟友埃诺克·戈东瓦纳担任财政部长，并表明他有意重振疲弱的经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/south-africa-elections-opposition-makes-debut-in-ramaphosa-s-unity-cabinet</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 20:19:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚总统为处理致命青年抗议事件辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/kenyan-president-defends-handling-of-deadly-youth-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托为其部署军队平息过去两周全国范围内抗议活动的决定进行辩护，抗议活动已造成至少 24 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/kenyan-president-defends-handling-of-deadly-youth-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 18:25:21 GMT</pubDate>
